action.description: The committee on HED recommend that the measure be PASSED, UNAMENDED. The votes were as follows: 7 Ayes: Representative(s) Garrett, Kapela, Kila, La Chica, Olds, Sayama, Muraoka; Ayes with reservations: none;  Noes: none; and 4 Excused: Representative(s) Amato, Evslin, Woodson, Souza.
